Package com.txtsoft.ftptrafficanalyzer

Application FTPTrafficAnalyzer - read out FTP host's log file, giving out a download click statistics to Java console.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FTPTrafficAnalyzer
    Compiler compliance level 11, so you need OpenJDK 11 or later separately installed to run the program.
    LogsFileAnalyzer
    Class provides functionality to extract information out of FTP server log files located as zipped files in FTP host's 'logs' directory.
    Utils
    Class contains some static members for general purpose.
